    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3201148544" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3201148544" />
    <a title="Kevin Lopez (on sabbatical)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/22976975-kevin-lopez-on-sabbatical"><img alt="Kevin Lopez (on sabbatical)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1376112680p2/22976975.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3201148544?book_show_action=true">Aug 11, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kevin Lopez (on sabbatical)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kevin Lopez (on sabbatical)" href="/user/show/22976975-kevin-lopez-on-sabbatical">Kevin Lopez (on sabbatical)</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover " href="/book/show/22448515-the-three-stigmata-of-palmer-eldritch">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22976975-kevin-lopez-on-sabbatical?shelf=fiction-thriller-crime-mystery">fiction-thriller-crime-mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22976975-kevin-lopez-on-sabbatical?shelf=sf-read">sf-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/22976975-kevin-lopez-on-sabbatical?shelf=sff-favorite-authors-philip-k-dick">sff-favorite-authors-philip-k-dick</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3201148544" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3066858212662391657">When should a 4.0 star book ever be rounded all the way up to 5.0 stars?? Probably only in the case of the weirdest PKD book I’ve ever read (and this is saying A LOT (although for a combination of pure weirdness and genius, “VALIS” still has it beat!)). <br/><br/>I finished this book last week and it still has me pondering the imponderables…</span>

          </span>
        </div>


